ly injects info into the \"stuck\" organism, which is simply recycling the same info over + over, with inevitable growth in entropy (disorder). This way explain why keep thinking of Valis as a computer or computer-like entity; it deals in info. (or even is info. Consider the significance for entropy/negentropy in the concept living info. Living info would (by virtu of being a biological organism - or like it overcome the entropic factor at its source in terms of information. So in a sense \"living info\" is (1) the ultimate life form; + (2) the ultimate solution to + foe of entropy. Let's say you could create anything you wanted in your universe. Wouldn't living info be it it by its nature would guaranted that your universe would not run down or devolve to a clockwork (machine) level or ossify (presuming the living info ie t 235 itself did not ossify or die; I guess it would have to be immortal. now, this happens to fit in with my binary switching-system in which effects exceed their cause + this I stipulate to be the indication par excellence of the presence of Christ. I called this insight my payoff insight, because here I equate Christ with newness, negentropy, life, change, growth + the antagonist of the mechanical. There is an immense logic to all this (summed up in the notion of the resurrection in which Christ not only returns to life but to a superior life!). Thus he is more than self-perpetuation He evolves, + radically. What Russ expresses in his letter has all sorts of implications for biological organization, the sub-assemblies forming separately (in disparate form) + then at the end coming together \"whereupon Christ is there for the first time.\" The Ditheon dream not only corroberates this but seemingly does so intentionally; this is the whole secret. It is impossible, but if you add two human psyches together you get Christ (that could, then, be expressed as \"Christ is a term we use for the successful com‐ bination - combining into a unity - of the 