      "text": "Last edit almost 3 years ago by svayambhu108\n152\nNeeds Review\n152\nK239 just to Xtianity (but Xtianity, as not are t Xtians, represented by the Platonist able to account for it, based on Plato's the i anamnesis + recovery of the Forms meta-abstraction by which the Forms are comprehended, Eckhart is the best example, but Augustine + Erigona are Okay, too). My post cards say \"in that case anamnesis of a previous life is not a previous life because previous' refers to time. + it is precisely the cat",
